cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine learning applications, specifically meta-learning and few-shot classification. These topics are commonly associated with sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
